  "title": "小团队做的 3 款产品月入 20 万美元，他们做对了什么？丨 Starter Story",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk5MDkxNDU4Nw==&mid=2247485186&idx=1&sn=d882d547274a1dc2c00ec92973dccd5c",
  "date": "2026-01-13 13:49:00",
  "author": "晚点再听LaterCast",
  "siteName": "晚点再听LaterCast",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=de42394c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FaubJvugmGm38ykibYV3GMCgOib19mwlzF0PDYDVnlbcJCvqWvPMaF0ibhNjmwIwpofkPlNTsiagV0XUsRZXOJLiclXw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h1 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">我们每天为你更新硅谷最新的 AI 创业与科技播客总结，让你与前沿保持同频。全文约 4000 字，如果你现在没有时间，试试转成播客稍后再听</span><a class=\"weapp_image_link js_weapp_entry\" data-miniprogram-type=\"image\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wxa4c5894e8895e7d1\" data-miniprogram-path=\"pages/player/player?podcastId=019bb796-4aa6-70ad-b03f-0a19a1717a5e&amp;openWithin=true\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"晚点再听LaterCast\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-applink=\"#小程序://晚点再听/qoHgDZfGcJead4f\" data-miniprogram-imageurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/aubJvugmGm3MsjfMGwQrW2XnYZL7jFzPEsY0zs7ZE3ibia8qyHxNv6PhXphfbSicwmRPa2JSibzZEO5Kvh1iaXtEsvA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"140\" data-backw=\"578\" data-ratio=\"0.24188790560471976\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-w=\"1017\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f807faf8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FaubJvugmGm3MsjfMGwQrW2XnYZL7jFzPEsY0zs7ZE3ibia8qyHxNv6PhXphfbSicwmRPa2JSibzZEO5Kvh1iaXtEsvA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></a></h1>\n  <h1 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">“在无聊的红海市场里，好的设计本身就是印钞机。”</span></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">“哪怕代码还没写完，你就应该开始写内容搞流量了。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">“免费用户只会浪费你的服务器，只有付费用户才会教你做产品。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在硅谷的叙事体系中，创业往往被描绘成一场要么成为十亿美金独角兽，要么彻底归零的豪赌。但来自澳大利亚的开发者 Mike 选择了第三条路。他手里握着 5 款 SaaS 产品（Curator, Frill, Juno, Fluke, Smile），没有拿过一分钱融资，团队极小，却实现了超过 20 万美元的月经常性收入（MRR）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Mike 的逻辑非常反直觉：他不追求改变世界，不追求颠覆性创新，甚至刻意回避那些看起来很酷的 AI 核心业务。他只做一件事：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">复制已经被验证过的“无聊”生意，用更好的设计和体验去抢占市场，并通过一套标准化的“10 步走剧本”将成功率拉满。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;对他来说，创业不是为了在这个行业里留下什么神话，而是为了能和喜欢的朋友一起工作，并且每个月都能分到丰厚的利润。这期内容，我们将拆解 Mike 这套“无法失败”的实战心法，看看在不依赖 VC 的情况下，普通开发者如何构建自己的现金流资产。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">1. 构建“无法失败”的商业模型</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">大多数初创公司死于“创始人内讧”或“资金链断裂”。Mike 为了规避这两个最大风险，设计了一套极度稳健的组织架构。他的目标非常明确：不融资、不寻求被大公司收购，而是在 5 年内实现 100 万美元 MRR，并将利润直接分给创始人。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在团队构成上，他坚持“4 人联合创始人”模型：1 个前端、1 个后端、1 个设计师，加上 1 个像他这样的全能型产品人。</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">股权分配上，他实行严格的 25% 均分制。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这在很多投资人眼里可能是不合理的（通常 CEO 会拿更多），但在 Mike 看来，这是减少内耗的最优解。当每个人都拥有平等的股份时，大家是真正的利益共同体，没有人会因为觉得“自己干得多拿得少”而心生怨怼。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">更吸引人的是他们的利润分配机制。当公司收入达到 1 万美元 MRR，足以覆盖服务器等基本成本后，剩余的所有利润都会作为薪水或分红发给创始人。</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">这是一种典型的“生活方式生意”（Lifestyle Business），它不承诺未来的百倍回报，但承诺当下的富足生活。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;此外，团队高度重视设计，因为“好的设计能卖钱”。在功能同质化的市场里，优秀的 UX 往往是用户选择你的唯一理由。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">2. 只做“无聊”但确定的生意</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Mike 承认自己早年做广告公司时是个糟糕的开发者，但他学会了最重要的商业直觉：风险控制。他的选品策略可以概括为“拒绝创新”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“新点子是有风险的，需要验证。如果你选了一个已经被做过的点子，你就知道人们确实想要它。你只需要做得比现有的产品好一点点。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果市面上已经有竞争对手，这反而是个好信号，说明需求是真实存在的。比如他的产品 Curator 是做社交媒体聚合的，Frill 是做客户反馈的，这些都是早已存在的红海市场。但他通过研究竞争对手，找出用户最想要的核心功能，剔除那些臃肿多余的部分，快速构建出一个“足够好”的 MVP（最小可行性产品）切入市场。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">值得注意的是，Mike 对 AI 持有非常谨慎的态度。</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">他明确表示绝不触碰纯 AI 核心的业务。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在他看来，如果你的核心价值建立在 OpenAI 等巨头的 API 之上，你就面临着巨大的“平台风险”。你的命运掌握在别人手里，API 一涨价，或者模型一更新，你的商业模式可能瞬间崩塌。他更倾向于做那些无论技术如何迭代，企业都必须用到的“水电煤”式工具。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">3. 用终身买断制（LTD）启动现金流</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">没有 VC 的钱，服务器和房租怎么付？Mike 的 10 步走剧本中，第 3 到第 5 步专门解决这个问题。他的核心武器是“终身交易”（Lifetime Deal，简称 LTD）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在产品刚上线时，他不会立刻开启订阅制，而是提供一个约 59 到 100 美元的一次性买断价格。对于早期用户来说，这是一个无法拒绝的诱惑；对于团队来说，这是宝贵的启动资金。以他的产品 Frill 为例，仅通过在 Reddit、Facebook 私密群组等私域社区销售 LTD，就筹集了 3 万美元。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个阶段，Mike 有一个铁律：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">绝不提供免费账户。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;很多人认为免费能换来增长，但 Mike 发现免费用户往往是最不活跃、反馈价值最低的群体。相反，只有掏了钱的用户（哪怕只是一次性付费），才会认真使用产品，并在遇到问题时给出严厉但有价值的反馈。这些真实的“吐槽”，是打磨 MVP 最好的磨刀石。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">4. 用预售资金换取分发渠道</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">拿到第一笔 LTD 收入后，Mike 并没有急着分红，而是进入了剧本的第 6 到第 8 步：扩大分发。他会把这笔钱投入到内容创作（SEO）中。他强调“永远不要嫌早”，在代码还在写的时候，就应该开始布局内容。策略非常直接：撰写“XX 产品的替代品” 页面和竞品对比文章。虽然 Google 收录和排名需要时间，但这是未来免费流量的基石。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">接着，他会利用 AppSumo 这样的大流量平台进行更大规模的分发。AppSumo 拥有巨大的用户库，非常适合 B2B 软件的冷启动。Mike 的目标非常具体：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">在 LTD 阶段结束时，公司账户里要存下 10 万美元现金。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这笔钱是团队未来 1 到 2 年的“跑道”，用于支付薪水、服务器和持续的内容支出，确保团队在没有订阅收入的情况下也能活下去。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 AppSumo 活动结束后，他会利用 FOMO（错失恐惧症）心理，向邮件列表发送“最后一次机会”的通知。小幅涨价，然后永久关闭 LTD 通道。这往往能带来最后的一波收入冲刺，同时也向用户宣告：产品已经成熟，即将进入正价订阅时代。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">5. 从一次性收入到订阅收入</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是整个剧本中生死攸关的时刻。LTD 虽然爽，但不可持续，公司最终必须靠 MRR（月经常性收入）活着。这时候，之前积累的数千名 LTD 用户就成了最好的资产，他们是你的早期大使。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“这是生死攸关的时刻。LTD 用户不仅提供了资金，更提供了社会证明。请求他们在 G2、Capterra、TrustPilot 上写真实评价，提升域名权重。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Mike 团队会请求这些用户去 G2、Capterra 等软件点评网站写下真实评价。这些“社会证明”对于后续转化订阅用户至关重要。同时，他们会扫描 Reddit，寻找那些在讨论竞争对手的用户，真诚地推荐自己的产品。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">随着 LTD 筹集的 10 万美元慢慢消耗，订阅收入必须逐步增长以接管成本。这是一个与时间赛跑的过程，当储备金耗尽前，MRR 必须能够覆盖团队开支。一旦跨过这个盈亏平衡点，公司就真正进入了“无法失败”的安全区。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">最后：创业是为了和朋友喝一杯</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Mike 的技术栈并不时髦，甚至有些复古：后端依然使用 PHP 和 Laravel，因为它们稳定高效；前端根据团队习惯选择 Vue 或 React。他将网站构建从开发团队剥离，交给设计运营人员用 Framer 完成，用 V0 和 Figma 快速出原型。一切为了效率，一切为了实用。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在访谈的最后，Mike 给出了他最朴素的建议：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“只和你愿意一起去酒吧喝一杯的人创业。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;赚钱固然重要，但如果不是为了和朋友一起做有趣的事，创业的艰辛会让你很难坚持下去。这种“工匠精神”，不仅通过产品赚钱，还要享受打磨细节的过程，或许才是他能够连续打造 5 款成功产品的真正秘诀。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">内容来源：“I Built 3 SaaS Apps to $200K MRR: Here's My Exact Playbook”丨Starter Story</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文拆解了开发者 Mike 如何通过复制已验证的“无聊”生意，利用 LTD 启动资金和标准化增长剧本，在不融资的情况下实现 20 万美元月收入的实战心法。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文拆解了开发者 Mike 如何通过复制已验证的“无聊”生意，利用 LTD 启动资金和标准化增长剧本，在不融资的情况下实现 20 万美元月收入的实战心法。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了澳大利亚开发者 Mike 的 SaaS 创业方法论。他主张避开高风险的颠覆性创新和纯 AI 核心业务，转而选择已被市场验证的“红海”领域，通过卓越的设计和用户体验进行差异化竞争。其核心策略包括：建立 4 人均分股权的稳定团队以减少内耗；利用终身买断制（LTD）在产品初期筹集启动资金并筛选高质量付费用户；通过 SEO 和 AppSumo 平台进行分发，积累 10 万美元现金储备作为“跑道”；最后利用早期用户的社会证明完成向订阅制（MRR）的平滑转型。这种“生活方式生意”模式强调效率、实用主义和团队和谐，为普通开发者提供了构建稳健现金流资产的可复制路径。",
